\f1\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl280
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl480

\f0\fs26 \cf2  \'a0\'a0\'93Oh poor dad is not feeling well, and he still came out to pick up your friends,\'94 Prashanth pretended to speak into the phone, \'93and his leg had still not healed, you better be thankful\'94. With that performance, he pretended to end the call and looked up at his father.\uc0\u8232 
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs26  \'a0\'a0\'a0"Pa shall I..." the words didn't come out confidently enough. Prashanth cleared his throat and tried again, "... Pa, can I drive?"
