\f0\fs26 \cf2  \'a0\'a0\'a0Before Mr. Menon could react, Prashanth darted up, turned around and jogged away from the seats mumbling something about checking the arrival time of the flight. He was walking fast enough to put himself out of ear-shot when Mr. Menon's words were finally ready for him. "
